1
00:01:59,120 --> 00:02:01,120
I'll give you one last chance.

2
00:02:02,560 --> 00:02:03,879
Later,

3
00:02:03,879 --> 00:02:05,359
during the medicinal bath round,

4
00:02:05,359 --> 00:02:07,120
while Yang Yunfan is picking his herbs,

5
00:02:07,120 --> 00:02:09,520
slip this into his medicinal bath.

6
00:02:09,759 --> 00:02:10,680
What is this?

7
00:02:12,120 --> 00:02:13,159
That's none of your concern.

8
00:02:13,680 --> 00:02:15,639
If he really is Number Zero,

9
00:02:15,639 --> 00:02:17,360
he'll definitely use the Sea-Pacifying Mind Art.

10
00:02:18,719 --> 00:02:19,680
But father...

11
00:02:19,680 --> 00:02:20,960
this is the entrance exam.

12
00:02:21,520 --> 00:02:23,240
Are you going to defy me again?

13
00:02:23,840 --> 00:02:24,319
Don't forget,

14
00:02:24,319 --> 00:02:25,919
you belong to the Lu Family.

15
00:02:27,840 --> 00:02:28,719
I...

16
00:02:34,719 --> 00:02:35,400
Mingcheng's back.

17
00:02:36,400 --> 00:02:37,400
Sit down.

18
00:02:42,319 --> 00:02:43,400
Have some water.

19
00:02:43,400 --> 00:02:44,879
Keep an eye on your sister for me.

20
00:02:47,680 --> 00:02:49,759
Slow down, it's hot.

21
00:02:49,759 --> 00:02:51,199
I'll make sure that kid

22
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:53,719
never makes it out alive.

23
00:03:03,319 --> 00:03:04,719
What?

24
00:03:04,719 --> 00:03:05,520
Can't bring yourself to do it?

25
00:03:08,560 --> 00:03:09,960
Don't tell me you actually fell for him.

26
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:15,800
I haven't.

27
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:16,599
You'd better not have.

28
00:03:17,560 --> 00:03:18,439
Don't forget,

29
00:03:18,439 --> 00:03:20,879
Father betrothed you to the Li Family.

30
00:03:22,400 --> 00:03:26,400
If you ruin my future for your feelings,

31
00:03:26,400 --> 00:03:27,000
don't blame me for being ruthless.

32
00:04:18,959 --> 00:04:19,600
Go, quick!

33
00:04:29,160 --> 00:04:29,800
Sandalwood.

34
00:04:29,800 --> 00:04:30,600
That'll teach you to be cocky.

35
00:04:33,519 --> 00:04:34,160
I'll poison you to death!

36
00:04:38,040 --> 00:04:38,480
Are you okay?

37
00:04:40,120 --> 00:04:40,560
I'm fine.

38
00:04:41,720 --> 00:04:42,519
Sis.

39
00:04:43,360 --> 00:04:45,600
You're the Li Family's future bride.

40
00:04:45,600 --> 00:04:46,800
Throwing yourself at another man?

41
00:04:48,480 --> 00:04:50,120
That's not very proper, is it?

42
00:04:54,120 --> 00:04:55,399
I didn't!

43
00:05:22,079 --> 00:05:23,199
There's something wrong with this water.

44
00:05:23,800 --> 00:05:24,879
I'll poison you to death!

45
00:05:41,560 --> 00:05:43,319
"Sea-Pacifying Mind Art."

46
00:05:50,040 --> 00:05:51,800
So it's from the Sea-Pacifying Mind Art,

47
00:05:51,800 --> 00:05:52,720
the Calming Heart Mantra.

48
00:05:53,199 --> 00:05:54,959
After being soaked in the Berserk Potion,

49
00:05:54,959 --> 00:05:57,040
only this can calm someone down quickly.

50
00:05:59,360 --> 00:06:01,120
So should we...

51
00:06:02,759 --> 00:06:03,560
Right.

52
00:06:04,240 --> 00:06:05,519
Pass on my order.

53
00:06:05,519 --> 00:06:07,160
Gather everyone in the Mystic Water Hall.

54
00:06:07,519 --> 00:06:08,839
That little thief, Number Zero,

55
00:06:09,160 --> 00:06:10,199
I've found him.

56
00:06:46,319 --> 00:06:47,000
Mind your own business.

57
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:51,839
Pill Master Lu just humiliated his sister.

58
00:06:51,839 --> 00:06:54,120
No need to come pretending to care now.

59
00:06:54,120 --> 00:06:55,240
No matter what,

60
00:06:55,600 --> 00:06:56,959
she's still a member of the Lu Family.

61
00:06:57,600 --> 00:06:59,199
She may belong to the Lu Family,

62
00:06:59,199 --> 00:07:00,879
but she's not your plaything or puppet.

63
00:07:06,879 --> 00:07:09,879
You dare cause trouble on Lu Family turf?

64
00:07:09,879 --> 00:07:11,519
You must have a death wish.

65
00:07:25,720 --> 00:07:26,920
Don't be in such a rush.

66
00:07:26,920 --> 00:07:28,720
It's the Lu Family's signature treatment.

67
00:07:28,720 --> 00:07:29,879
Soak in it for a while first.

68
00:07:32,680 --> 00:07:33,600
Just you wait.

69
00:07:33,600 --> 00:07:34,600
Don't run if you've got the guts.

70
00:08:04,720 --> 00:08:07,560
I thought you were all talk.

71
00:08:07,560 --> 00:08:09,959
I didn't expect you to be so caring.

72
00:08:20,240 --> 00:08:21,600
What are you afraid of?

73
00:08:21,600 --> 00:08:23,480
I don't care about your scrawny body.

74
00:08:25,199 --> 00:08:27,000
You passed the test just now.

75
00:08:30,439 --> 00:08:32,360
Get changed and come with me.

76
00:08:35,399 --> 00:08:36,200
Yunfan.

77
00:08:40,600 --> 00:08:41,840
Don't worry.

78
00:08:41,840 --> 00:08:43,200
No challenge can ever stump me.

79
00:09:09,440 --> 00:09:10,720
The final trial

80
00:09:10,720 --> 00:09:11,519
The Path of Reverence

81
00:09:12,399 --> 00:09:14,480
Sincerely bow to the Medicine Venerable

82
00:09:14,480 --> 00:09:16,559
And swear to abide by the Medicine Venerable's teachings

83
00:09:25,399 --> 00:09:27,759
A free-spirited healer walks the path

84
00:09:27,759 --> 00:09:29,799
Doing good deeds without seeking fame

85
00:09:29,799 --> 00:09:31,440
Heal by following your true heart

86
00:09:31,440 --> 00:09:32,799
Never crave glory or renown

87
00:09:33,720 --> 00:09:35,120
Haven't I said this somewhere before?

88
00:09:35,720 --> 00:09:36,559
Why does it sound so familiar?

89
00:09:40,720 --> 00:09:41,840
He's here! Grab him!

90
00:09:42,879 --> 00:09:43,840
You little thief!

91
00:09:44,200 --> 00:09:45,200
Don't you dare move!

92
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:47,200
What are you...

93
00:09:47,200 --> 00:09:47,879
Pharmacy Master Lu

94
00:09:48,960 --> 00:09:50,000
What is the meaning of this?

95
00:09:51,320 --> 00:09:53,720
Is he the fake Number Zero from before?

96
00:09:54,480 --> 00:09:55,679
Honored Medicine Venerable

97
00:09:55,679 --> 00:09:58,879
Disciple Lu Daozai meant no disturbance,

98
00:09:58,879 --> 00:10:01,240
But the thief who stole Mystic Water Hall's text,

99
00:10:01,240 --> 00:10:03,360
the Sea-Pacifying Mind Art, is right here.

100
00:10:03,360 --> 00:10:04,200
This disciple had no other choice.

101
00:10:04,639 --> 00:10:05,480
A thief?

102
00:10:05,960 --> 00:10:07,360
Pharmacy Master Lu, you don't mean me?

103
00:10:07,720 --> 00:10:09,000
Glad you know it.

104
00:10:09,000 --> 00:10:09,759
You little thief!

105
00:10:09,759 --> 00:10:11,679
Hand over the Sea-Pacifying Mind Art now!

106
00:10:11,679 --> 00:10:12,480
You old geezer!

107
00:10:12,480 --> 00:10:13,399
What proof do you have?

108
00:10:13,720 --> 00:10:14,600
Proof?

109
00:10:15,559 --> 00:10:18,240
The hand seal you used in the bath...

110
00:10:18,240 --> 00:10:19,519
If this Pharmacy Master isn't mistaken,

111
00:10:20,279 --> 00:10:22,039
that was from the Sea-Pacifying Mind Art:

112
00:10:22,039 --> 00:10:24,639
the Calming Heart Mantra for inner peace.

113
00:10:25,519 --> 00:10:26,240
That's right.

114
00:10:26,240 --> 00:10:28,639
Pharmacy Master Lu wouldn't misremember.

115
00:10:28,639 --> 00:10:30,960
He actually mastered it!

116
00:10:30,960 --> 00:10:32,360
By your logic,

117
00:10:32,360 --> 00:10:34,480
anyone using this seal is a book thief?

118
00:10:34,480 --> 00:10:35,840
There are countless healers in this world.

119
00:10:35,840 --> 00:10:37,240
Would you brand them all as thieves?

120
00:10:38,240 --> 00:10:39,519
Argue all you want.

121
00:10:39,519 --> 00:10:41,919
But the Sea-Pacifying Mind Art

122
00:10:41,919 --> 00:10:44,879
is the secret art of the Yang Family, former masters of Mystic Water Hall.

123
00:10:44,879 --> 00:10:46,720
After the Yang Family was wiped out,

124
00:10:46,720 --> 00:10:48,200
only one copy remained in this world.

125
00:10:48,200 --> 00:10:50,240
Kept safely by Green Wood Hall all along.

126
00:10:50,240 --> 00:10:52,960
Only shown at the Mystic Healers Summit.

127
00:10:53,919 --> 00:10:55,840
Aside from the one who stole the Sea-Pacifying Mind Art,

128
00:10:55,840 --> 00:10:56,759
the little thief Number Zero,

129
00:10:56,759 --> 00:10:58,639
no one else could possibly learn this art.

130
00:10:58,639 --> 00:11:01,960
Therefore, this man is Number Zero.

131
00:11:02,960 --> 00:11:04,440
So you've never seen the Calming Heart Mantra?

132
00:11:05,320 --> 00:11:07,159
And just now you sounded so certain.

133
00:11:07,159 --> 00:11:08,720
You dare smear me without ever seeing it?

134
00:11:08,720 --> 00:11:09,639
Who gave you the nerve?

135
00:11:09,639 --> 00:11:10,320
Shut up!

136
00:11:10,759 --> 00:11:12,799
In Mystic Water Hall, my word is law.

137
00:11:12,799 --> 00:11:13,360
Take him away.

138
00:11:14,399 --> 00:11:15,320
Who dares?

139
00:11:36,519 --> 00:11:38,039
Yang Yunfan

140
00:11:38,039 --> 00:11:40,639
is the fiancé chosen by the Medicine Venerable.

141
00:11:41,360 --> 00:11:42,759
As a descendant of the Yang Family,

142
00:11:42,759 --> 00:11:44,720
for him to hold the Sea-Pacifying Mind Art...

143
00:11:44,720 --> 00:11:46,240
Isn't that only natural?

144
00:11:46,919 --> 00:11:48,639
What? He's a descendant of the Yang Family?

145
00:11:48,639 --> 00:11:50,320
But wasn't the Yang Family wiped out back then?

146
00:11:53,240 --> 00:11:54,399
Miss Ye,

147
00:11:54,399 --> 00:11:57,080
You claim this man is of the Yang Family.

148
00:11:57,799 --> 00:11:58,559
What proof do you have?

149
00:12:15,240 --> 00:12:16,919
This is what Grandfather

150
00:12:16,919 --> 00:12:19,639
forged as an engagement token for us.

151
00:12:24,519 --> 00:12:27,399
Yang Yunfan is my designated fiancé,

152
00:12:28,039 --> 00:12:30,039
and the sole heir of the Yang Family,

153
00:12:30,519 --> 00:12:32,039
of the legitimate Yang Family bloodline.

154
00:12:32,759 --> 00:12:34,759
If anyone dares to question this again,

155
00:12:35,919 --> 00:12:37,519
they'll be questioning me, Ye Qingxue.

156
00:12:41,480 --> 00:12:42,600
Come here.

157
00:12:45,120 --> 00:12:46,240
In that case,

158
00:12:46,720 --> 00:12:48,320
we'll let it go for today.

159
00:12:49,360 --> 00:12:50,240
Let's go.

160
00:12:53,240 --> 00:12:55,159
You didn't even look at

161
00:12:55,159 --> 00:12:56,519
who has my back.

162
00:12:59,039 --> 00:13:00,120
Don't push your luck.

163
00:13:01,879 --> 00:13:02,960
So cool.
